<P>
Thanks for spoiling my breakfast as I read the article about televangelist Pat 
Robertson forming a political coalition (Part A, May 15). The American voters 
resoundingly rejected his right-wing agenda when he ran for president and he's 
going to attempt to shove it down our throats again. 
</P>
