<P>
Campbell to Sell Some European Units: Campbell Soup Co. said it plans to sell 
several of its European food units in an effort to focus on its more profitable 
businesses. 
</P>
<P>
On the block are D. Lazzaroni &amp; C. S.p.A. of Italy; Campbell Seafoods 
division, which operates in the United Kingdom and Belgium; the vegetable 
division of Campbell Foods PLC in England, and Campbell Irish Foods Ltd. and 
Mallow Foods Ltd., both of Ireland. Total sales of all the businesses to be 
