<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA052890-0103 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 225632 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 28, 1990, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 18; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
