<P>
An anti-obscenity pledge that must be signed by artists receiving grants from 
the National Endowment for the Arts has been mandated by the NEA. In some 
editions of Saturday Calendar, it incorrectly was reported that the pledge was 
mandated by Congress. 
</P>
